[% [:en] requirements[![^:oc Hash]]
   [:zh_CN] 规定[![^:oc Hash]] ]
[para]
[:en]
A type [`H] meets the [^:oc Hash] requirements if:
[:zh_CN]
若满足下列条件，则类型 [`H] 满足 [^:oc Hash] 规定：

[list]
[item]
[:en] it is a function object type ([#function.objects]),
[:zh_CN] 它是函数对象类型（[#function.objects]），
[item]
[:en] it meets the [^:oc CopyConstructible] ([#:tab#cpp17.copyconstructible])
and [^:oc Destructible] ([#:tab#cpp17.destructible]) requirements, and
[:zh_CN] 它满足 [^:oc CopyConstructible]（[#:tab#cpp17.copyconstructible]）和
[^:oc Destructible]（[#:tab#cpp17.destructible]）的规定，并且
[item]
[:en] the expressions shown in [#:tab#cpp17.hash] are valid and have the
indicated semantics.
[:zh_CN] [#:tab#cpp17.hash] 中列出的表达式均合法，且具有所指定的语义。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en]
Given [`Key] is an argument type for function objects of type [`H], in
[#:tab#cpp17.hash] [`h] is a value of type (possibly [`const]) [`H], [`u] is an
lvalue of type [`Key], and [`k] is a value of a type convertible to (possibly
[`const]) [`Key].
[:zh_CN]
给定 [`Key] 为类型 [`H] 的函数对象的实参类型，[#:tab#cpp17.hash] 中的 [`h] 为
类型（可能为 [`const] 的）[`H] 的值，[`u] 为类型 [`Key] 的左值，而 [`k] 为可以
转换为（可能为 [`const] 的）[`Key] 的值。

